, N'prapya--after achieving; punya-krtam--of those who performed pious activities; lokan--planets; usitva--after dwelling; sasvatih--many; samah--years; sucinam--of the pious; sri-matam--of the prosperous;gehe--in the house of; yoga-bhrastah--one who is fallen from the path of self-realization; abhijayate--takes his birth.'
